Rating

Product Description:

If you want to be a professional cocktail mixer, then you've got to start somewhere. The Manhattan Cocktail Shaker Set contains enough cocktail accessories to help you on your way to a future of drinks mixing. Great for parties, this set includes; a 28oz Manhattan Cocktail Shaker, Hawthorne Cocktail Strainer, Wooden Cocktail Muddler, Twisted Mixing Spoon, 25ml Thimble Measure, 50ml Thimble Measure. Please Note: drinkstuff is the only official seller of the copyrighted bar@drinkstuff product range. Dimensions: Manhattan Cocktail Shaker: H 260mm Ø 90mm Hawthorne Cocktail Strainer: L 150mm W 115mm Book: H 165mm W 115mm D 13mmMuddler: L 210mm Ø 25mmTwisted Mixing Spoon: L 280mm W 35mm D 32mm25ml Bar Measure: H 39mm Ø 38mm 50ml Bar Measure: H 64mm Ø 38mm
